sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant P as Program
    participant S as Scripture
    participant R as Reference
    participant W as Word

    U->>P: Start Program
    P->>R: Create Reference
    P->>S: Create Scripture(reference, text)
    S->>W: Create Words from text
    
    loop Until quit or complete
        P->>S: GetDisplayText()
        S->>R: GetDisplayText()
        S->>W: GetDisplayText() for each word
        P->>U: Display Scripture
        U->>P: Press Enter/Quit
        alt Enter Pressed
            P->>S: HideRandomWords()
            S->>W: Hide() selected words
        end
    end